Function calling tasks evaluate the LLM’s ability to effectively use external APIs/tools to perform
user-speciﬁed tasks. We evaluate function calling capabilities of different models using the following
public benchmarks, namely Berkeley Function-Calling Leaderboard
et al., 2023c), API-Bench (Patil et al., 2023), ToolAlpaca (Tang et al., 2023), Nexus (Srinivasan et al.,
2023), SealTools (Wu et al., 2024), and API-Bench (Patil et al., 2023).
